trans-unit.source: Abstract base class for the channel dispatcher that accepts channels and associates them with a service.
trans-unit.target: Abstrakt basklass för kanal-dispatcher som accepterar kanaler som associeras med en tjänst.

trans-unit.source: This is used by developers who want to keep the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming model but replace the system-provided runtime.
trans-unit.target: Det här används av utvecklare som vill behålla den [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programmering modell men ersätt systembaserade körningsmiljön.

trans-unit.source: Such applications will pull messages out of channels and handle them directly with user-defined dispatchers.
trans-unit.target: Sådana program använder meddelanden utanför kanaler och hantera dem direkt med användardefinierade avsändare.

trans-unit.source: To use ChannelDispatcherBase , create a class derived from it, extend <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> and override <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adding instances of your class derived from ChannelDispatcherBase to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Att använda ChannelDispatcherBase, skapa en klass som härletts från den, utöka <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>och åsidosätta <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, lägga till instanser av klassen härleds från ChannelDispatcherBase till <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, associated with the ChannelDispatcherBase object are available for inspection or modification through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> respectively.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, associerade med objektet ChannelDispatcherBase är tillgängliga för inspektion eller modifiering via den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A>respektive.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> methods when adding or removing a ChannelDispatcherBase item from its <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>anrop av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29>metoder när du lägger till eller tar bort en ChannelDispatcherBase objektet från dess <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samling.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29></xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A> during shutdown before closing InstanceContexts.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>anrop av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A>vid avstängningen innan du stänger InstanceContexts.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A></xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] uses this call to close datagram channels and wait for all messages to get to an InstanceContext.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]använder det här anropet för att stänga datagram kanaler och vänta tills alla meddelanden till en InstanceContext.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, attaches the channel dispatcher to a specific host.
trans-unit.target: Bifogar dispatcher kanal till en viss värd när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: This method can only be set when the instance of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> is in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> state, as this is the only state that is both mutable and not disposed.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan endast anges när instansen av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState>eftersom det är bara Tillståndet som både föränderliga och inte borttaget tillstånd.</xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls this method when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> is added to its <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>anropar den här metoden när den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>läggs till dess <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samling.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: This gives the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> a chance to hook events and inspect the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, and provides the value that should be returned from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Detta ger den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>möjlighet att koppla händelser och inspektera de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, och ger det värde som ska returneras från den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, tar du bort endpoint-avsändare som är associerad med kanalen dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls this method during shutdown to give the dispatcher a chance to drain messages.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>anropar den här metoden under avstängning att ge dispatcher en möjlighet att tömma meddelanden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> uses this call to close datagram channels.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>använder det här anropet för att stänga datagram kanaler.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, detaches the channel dispatcher from a specific host.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, tar du bort kanal dispatcher från en viss värd.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> can only be detached when the instance of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> is in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> state, as this is the only state that is both mutable and not disposed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>kan bara kopplas när instansen av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState>eftersom det är bara Tillståndet som både föränderliga och inte borttaget tillstånd.</xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.source: Should set the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> associated with the channel dispatcher to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Måste ange den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>som är associerad med kanalen dispatcher till `null`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.target: Hämtar värden för tjänsten som är associerad med kanalen dispatcher när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> object can have many <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> objects, each associated with a different <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> for that service.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>objekt kan ha många <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>objekt, var och en som är associerade med en annan <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>för tjänsten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: The host keeps a list of these <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> objects in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Värden har en lista över dessa <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>objekt i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samling.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"></xref> for the service associated with the dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"> </xref> för tjänsten som är associerade med dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the channel listener associated with the channel dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar kanallyssnaren som är associerad med kanalen dispatcher när åsidosätts i en härledd klass.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> associates an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> whose channels and messages this <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> is dispatching.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>associerar en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>vars kanaler och meddelanden om detta <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>är sändning.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener"></xref> associated with the channel dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener"> </xref> som är associerad med kanalen dispatcher.
